gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Take heed of your eldest son who has become too big-headed, for this will ultimately lead to great sacrifice; 
See from today what is his downfall, and know that there is no point in lamenting what cannot be done.

Here is the translation:

Listen to her voice so carefully, write down all inner thoughts so carefully;
He has knowledge of virtues, his virtues have made him equal to her.
